## What is FYT Auto Clicker?

FYT Auto Clicker is a software designed to automate mouse clicks on desktops and laptops. It simulates mouse clicks at a pre-determined location on the screen, freeing up users to focus on other tasks. The software is compatible with Windows 7, 8, and 10.

## How Does FYT Auto Clicker Work?

FYT Auto Clicker is easy to use. Users can set the location of the mouse clicks, the frequency of clicks, and the duration of the clicks. The software will then perform the clicks at the set location and interval.

The software also comes with a feature that allows users to record mouse clicks. This feature is helpful when users need to perform the same clicks repeatedly.
